OL,2,MThe automation wars... One marriage,
OL,4,Mtwo tech philosophies
OL,6,CRosa Morgan-Baker and Arthur Guy
OL,7,CSun 13:20-13:50
OL,8,CStage B
OL,10,GMy husband and I have been together
OL,11,Gfor 19 years, since meeting at
OL,12,Guniversity. We’re opposites in many
OL,13,Gways but have somehow made it work. He
OL,14,Gloves salt popcorn, I prefer sweet. He
OL,15,Genjoys plays, I love musicals. He’s a
OL,16,Gtechnologist; I’m far more analogue
OL,17,Gand would happily turn a bathroom
OL,18,Glight on without an app. Yet we now
OL,19,Glive in a home with more than 200
OL,20,Gsensors, automations and connected
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
